original_title: Demon Hunter Songs - Songs of Death and Resurrection Livestream
overview: Songs of Death and Resurrection, a brand new album featuring lush acoustic arrangements of classic Demon Hunter songs (including "I Will Fail You," "Dead Flowers," "The Heart of a Graveyard," and more), plus a new song, "Praise the Void." We will perform the entire album via Livestream on Nov 20th 5pm PS
title: Demon Hunter Songs - Songs of Death and Resurrection Livestream
